WORKDIR code

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir virtualenv
RUN virtualenv ve && /code/ve/bin/pip install -U pip
RUN /code/ve/bin/pip install -r /code/requirements.txt
RUN /code/ve/bin/pip install -r /code/test_requirements.txt
WORKDIR /code/docb
